TI  - Do an ecosystem engineer and environmental gradient act independently or in concert to shape juvenile plant communities? Tests with the leaf-cutter ant Atta laevigata in a Neotropical savanna
T2  - PEERJ
KW  - Atta
KW  - Seedling
KW  - Herbivory
KW  - Gradient
