TI  - Multiple successional pathways in human-modified tropical landscapes: new insights from forest succession, forest fragmentation and landscape ecology research
T2  - BIOLOGICAL REVIEWS
KW  - biodiversity conservation
KW  - ecosystem services
KW  - forest recovery
KW  - landscape structure
