TI  - RURAL SETTLEMENT SCHEMES IN THE SOUTH WEST OF WESTERN AUSTRALIA AND RORAIMA STATE, BRAZIL: UNSUSTAINABLE RURAL SYSTEMS?
T2  - CARPATHIAN JOURNAL OF EARTH AND ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCES
KW  - Rural settlement schemes
KW  - group settlement: Nova Amazonia
KW  - Western Australia
KW  - Roraima
