TI  - Modeling spatial decisions with graph theory: logging roads and forest fragmentation in the Brazilian Amazon
T2  - ECOLOGICAL APPLICATIONS
KW  - Amazonia
KW  - forest fragmentation
KW  - graph theory
KW  - logging
KW  - LAND-COVER
