TI  - Ant fauna (Hymenoptera, Formicidae) associated to arboreal nests of Nasutitermes spp. (Isoptera, Termitidae) in a cacao plantation in southeastern Bahia, Brazil
T2  - REVISTA BRASILEIRA DE ENTOMOLOGIA
KW  - Agricultural forest system
KW  - diversity
KW  - nesting
KW  - Theobroma cacao
