TI  - Testing for the influence of niche and neutral factors on sapling community assembly beneath isolated woody plants in grasslands
T2  - JOURNAL OF VEGETATION SCIENCE
KW  - Araucaria forest
KW  - Campos grassland
KW  - Canonical correspondence analysis
KW  - Nursing effect
KW  - Perching effect
KW  - ABANDONED TROPICAL PASTURE
KW  - EXPLAINING BETA DIVERSITY
