TI  - The use of phytosociology in effective evaluation of forest restoration in a Mogi Guacu River degraded floodplain, Sao Paulo, Brazil
T2  - SCIENTIA FORESTALIS
KW  - Riparian forest
KW  - Reforestation
KW  - Diversity index
